# ---- Confidential data ----
# Defensive: the 2023 oracle xlsx lives outside the repo at ~/Desktop/RA/
# conf_2023_test.xlsx and must NEVER enter any commit. Block all .xlsx as
# belt-and-braces — see CLAUDE.md §2.1 / §4.3 / §7.1.
*.xlsx
*.xls

# ---- R / RStudio ----
.Rhistory
.Rapp.history
.RData
.Ruserdata
.Rproj.user/

# R session temp files
.RDataTmp

# ---- macOS junk ----
.DS_Store
._*
.Spotlight-V100
.Trashes
.AppleDouble
.LSOverride

# ---- Large regenerable API snapshots ----
# Edmonton Property Information API (dkk9-cj3x) — refetch via the loader script.
# Patterns use **/data/... so they match at any section depth
# (e.g. pipeline/property-assessment/data/...) per CLAUDE.md §3.
**/data/raw/property_info_*.csv

# Large derived outputs — regenerable from scripts 01, 03, 06.
# Excluded for size (GitHub 100 MB hard limit) and to keep the
# validation export out of public distribution.
**/data/processed/assess_*.csv
**/data/validation/edmonton_row_labels_2023.csv

